All modules are optional.  
All modules are replaceable.

The system is designed to survive partial failure.

---

## Core Modules

### Coordination API
- Entry point for all actions  
- Governance rules  
- Role & permission checks  

### Reputation Engine
- Non-financial scoring  
- Behavior & consistency tracking  
- Visibility weighting  

### Feedback Loop
- User reports  
- Event feedback  
- Pattern detection  

### Automation Layer
- Cron jobs  
- Workers  
- Reward distribution  
- Penalty logic  

---

## Policy Modules (City AI Concept)

### FLS (Financial Logic Shield)
- Filters high-risk actions  
- Enforces system constraints  

### CES (Engagement System)
- Measures community friction & engagement  

### Police Module
- Detects abuse patterns  
- Flags anomalous behavior  

### Mayor Module
- Adjusts global policy parameters  

### Council Module
- Dispatch hub for policy decisions  

---

## External Modules

### Broker Interface
- Trade execution  
- Deposit handling  
- Withdrawal handling  

### Donation / Disaster Autopilot
- Event detection  
- Allocation logic  
- Audit trails  

---

## Replaceability

Each module can be:

- removed  
- swapped  
- rewritten  

without breaking the core coordination layer.
